---
title: Classic Chicken & Bacon Parmigiana with Totara Cheddar & Roast Veggie Salad
description: Who doesn’t love a good parmigiana? Take it to new levels by adding a roasted veggie salad for a hit of freshness and bake it in a thick gooey layer of Cheddar cheese and bacon, this tomato coated and golden crumbed chicken will definitely be the star of the evening.
